ballot_measures.number: Changes to Budget Stabilization Fund Amendment
ballot_measures.title: Changes to Budget Stabilization Fund Amendment
ballot_measures.description: Increase the amount of funds that may be retained in the budget stabilization fund from 10% to 25% of net general revenue among other changes. This legislatively referred constitutional amendment is on the Florida 2026 ballot.

ballot_measures.number: Exempt Tangible Personal Property Used for Agriculture or Agritourism from Property Taxes Amendment
ballot_measures.title: Exempt Tangible Personal Property Used for Agriculture or Agritourism from Property Taxes Amendment
ballot_measures.description: Exempt agricultural-related tangible personal property, such as farm equipment or tools, from property taxes. This legislatively referred constitutional amendment is on the Florida 2026 ballot.
